---

🎨 DESIGN SYSTEM (OPTION 3)

Visual style = calm, elegant, minimal, emotionally healing.

• Use soft gradients  
• Ample whitespace  
• Clean hierarchy  
• Responsive typography  
• Modularity-first for reuse in Webflow or Framer

---

🌈 BRAND COLORS

```css
--sage: #8fbf9f;
--sage-light: rgba(143, 191, 159, 0.1);
--rose: #f4c7c3;
--deep-teal: #2f5d5d;
--cream: #faf9f7;
